PREREQUISITE
-----------

terraform version -- Terraform v1.0.6

create u r own sshkey copy the idrsa.pb key into folder scripts file web.pub  -- /scripts/web.pub

configure awscli i have used region us-east-1 

terraform init -- will intilaise terraform plugin and configure s3 backend 

i have uesd terraform workspace to craete the iac in dev environment to use as it is run followin commands 

terraform workspace new dev

to switch into dev workspace

terrafrom workspace select dev

to verify run  command

terraform workspace show

to run test of u r scripts run validate

terraform valiadte 

to see the exection of iac run plan

terraform plan

to apply iac 

terraform apply -auto-approve

TOTALLY IT WILL CREATE 29 RESOURCES


